; LedgerRow — pattern #10 from interaction-patterns.md.
; Parchment sub-panel register used INSIDE a larger panel (e.g., Guild Hall
; HeroCards inside the RosterPanel). Visual register: a row in a guild
; ledger book. Hairline 1px Slate Ink border at 50% alpha (subtle separator,
; not full panel border); 2px corner radius (rigid ledger-row feel); compact
; 8px padding. Apply via card.theme_type_variation = &"LedgerRow".
; Sprint 20 S20-M5 (2026-05-15) addition.
[sub_resource type="StyleBoxFlat" id="ledger_row"]
